01, \"end\": 6912, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Legend\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"John Legend\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Legend\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/John_Legend\"}, {\"begin\": 6914, \"end\": 6926, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebel_Wilson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Rebel Wilson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebel_Wilson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rebel_Wilson\"}, {\"begin\": 6928, \"end\": 6939, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_DeVine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Adam Devine\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_DeVine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Adam_DeVine\"}, {\"begin\": 6945, \"end\": 6960, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_Handler\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Chelsea Handler\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_Handler\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Chelsea_Handler\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Most recently, Cooper launched media company, Trending and its subsidiary, The Unwell Network, alongside her partner Matt Kaplan of ACE Entertainment.\", \"from\": 6977, \"to\": 7127, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7056, \"end\": 7062, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unwell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Unwell\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unwell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unwell\"}, {\"begin\": 7094, \"end\": 7105, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Kaplan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Matt Kaplan\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Kaplan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Matt_Kaplan\"}, {\"begin\": 7109, \"end\": 7112, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Cinema_Editors\", \"score\": 0.9999999934534571, \"rank\": 6.395157498717793e-09, \"text\": \"ACE\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Cinema_Editors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/American_Cinema_Editors\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This media venture is elevating the voices and stories of Gen Z.\", \"from\": 7128, \"to\": 7192, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7186, \"end\": 7191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Generation_Z\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Gen Z\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Generation_Z\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Generation_Z\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Unwell Network's initial talent signings include top creators and influencers Alix Earle, Madeline Argy, and Harry Jowsey, who are working with Cooper and the Unwell team to develop a variety of multiplatform concepts and projects.\", \"from\": 7193, \"to\": 7428, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7275, \"end\": 7279, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Adventures_of_Alix\", \"score\": 0.9999999809833755, \"rank\": 1.3714090557778695e-08, \"text\": \"Alix\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q245068\", \"Q234460\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Adventures_of_Alix\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/The_Adventures_of_Alix\"}, {\"begin\": 7287, \"end\": 7295, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madeline\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.095052671671836e-37, \"text\": \"Madeline\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madeline\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Madeline\"}, {\"begin\": 7296, \"end\": 7300, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argy\", \"score\": 0.8350804352517057, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Argy\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argy\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Argy\"}, {\"begin\": 7356, \"end\": 7362, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unwell\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Unwell\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q2188189\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unwell\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Unwell\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Notable accolades for Cooper include TIME's 2023 TIME100 Next List, Rolling Stone's 2023 - The 20 Most Influential Creators Right Now, Forbes 30 Under 30 in Media 2022, Forbes Top Creators of 2022, Fortune 40 Under 40 in 2022, Variety Hollywood's New Leaders of 2021, E!\", \"from\": 7430, \"to\": 7700, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7467, \"end\": 7471, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Top_International_Managers_in_Engineering\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2814145209985237e-17, \"text\": \"TIME\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Top_International_Managers_in_Engineering\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Top_International_Managers_in_Engineering\"}, {\"begin\": 7479, \"end\": 7491, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_100\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"TIME100 Next\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_100\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Time_100\"}, {\"begin\": 7498, \"end\": 7511, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.503359966262511e-25, \"text\": \"Rolling Stone\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Rolling_Stone\"}, {\"begin\": 7599, \"end\": 7605, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Forbes\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.708827977105046e-39, \"text\": \"Forbes\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Forbes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/reso