s, DreamWorks Animation and Illumination; next-day access to all new shows from NBC and Bravo; fan-favorite library content; daily live news; as well as live channels from brands including Hallmark and WWE.\", \"from\": 7986, \"to\": 8443, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 8204, \"end\": 8222, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Universal_Pictures\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 7.342940723360348e-19, \"text\": \"Universal Pictures\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Universal_Pictures\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Universal_Pictures\"}, {\"begin\": 8224, \"end\": 8238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Focus_Features\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Focus Features\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Focus_Features\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Focus_Features\"}, {\"begin\": 8317, \"end\": 8320, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999999999990905, \"rank\": 7.083448933036788e-13, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}, {\"begin\": 8325, \"end\": 8330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.2404086502264817e-23, \"text\": \"Bravo\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/CTV_Drama_Channel\"}, {\"begin\": 8426, \"end\": 8434, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hallmark_Channel\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.4211704672251887e-15, \"text\": \"Hallmark\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hallmark_Channel\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Hallmark_Channel\"}, {\"begin\": 8439, \"end\": 8442, \"title\